  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Determine the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics, maximum tolerated dose (MTD) and
      recommended phase 2 dose (RP2D) of BAY 1251152 in patients with solid tumors and aggressive
      non-hodgkin's lymphoma (NHL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
